    <p class="p_Task" style="page-break-inside: avoid; page-break-after: avoid; border-top: none; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; border-left: none;"><span class="f_Task">Position l&ouml;schen (Biegeform, Formstahl- oder Formmatten)</span></p>

